  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Dagdrøm</strong></i> is a challenging old school adventure game, inspired by classics like <i>Monkey Island</i>, <i>Broken Sword</i> and <i>Machinarium</i>, but with some new twists and turns. Fear not: The game comes with a simple in-game hint system and a visual walkthrough guide. It is available for Windows PC, Mac and Linux.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The sun rises. The good people of this zone wake up from their slumber only to find that the city reserves of <i>The Dream Tea</i>, a favoured refreshment in these parts, has run empty. Its main ingredient? <i>The Dream Juice</i>, a mystical black extract, somehow connected to that tower on the horizon…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel across desert dunes towards <i>The Great Tower</i> to find questions, answers and most importantly: something to drink. Survive mysterious separatists, face <i>The Stone Golem</i> and cook a wide selection of broth based soups… That is: If you can get a ticket on a train in the first place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic point-and-click gameplay with a simple modern interface</li><li>Three act storyline, each with a distinct setting</li><li>A cast of over twenty characters, each with frame-by-frame hand drawn animations</li><li>Original soundtrack</li><li>Full HD resolution</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/3da5198a07148c5e5e57b83c815ba40b.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Dagdrøm</strong></i> is a challenging old school adventure game, inspired by classics like <i>Monkey Island</i>, <i>Broken Sword</i> and <i>Machinarium</i>, but with some new twists and turns. Fear not: The game comes with a simple in-game hint system and a visual walkthrough guide. It is available for Windows PC, Mac and Linux.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/5834c5e2aa7d678f7d51a0e86c925887.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The sun rises. The good people of this zone wake up from their slumber only to find that the city reserves of <i>The Dream Tea</i>, a favoured refreshment in these parts, has run empty. Its main ingredient? <i>The Dream Juice</i>, a mystical black extract, somehow connected to that tower on the horizon…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.poster.avif?t=1708610683\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.webm?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148880/extras/751d964dc5d048da3b6d8a142132cfa7.mp4?t=1708610683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel across desert dunes towards <i>The Great Tower</i> to find questions, answers and most importantly: something to drink. Survive mysterious separatists, face <i>The Stone Golem</i> and cook a wide selection of broth based soups… That is: If you can get a ticket on a train in the first place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic point-and-click gameplay with a simple modern interface</li><li>Three act storyline, each with a distinct setting</li><li>A cast of over twenty characters, each with frame-by-frame hand drawn animations</li><li>Original soundtrack</li><li>Full HD resolution</li></ul>",
